10720010@unknown@formal@none@1@S@<article>RapidMiner</article>@1@1@@oe@30-11-2008
10720020@unknown@formal@none@1@S@'''RapidMiner''' (formerly YALE (Yet Another Learning Environment)) is an environment for [[machine learning]] and [[data mining]] experiments.@1@17@@oe@30-11-2008
10720030@unknown@formal@none@1@S@It allows experiments to be made up of a large number of arbitrarily nestable operators, described in [[XML]] files which can easily be created with RapidMiner's [[graphical user interface]].@1@29@@oe@30-11-2008
