10720070@unknown@formal@none@1@S@RapidMiner provides more than 400 operators for all main machine learning procedures, including input and output, and data preprocessing and visualization.@1@21@@oe@30-11-2008
10720080@unknown@formal@none@1@S@It is written in the [[Java (programming language)|Java programming language]] and therefore can work on all popular operating systems.@1@19@@oe@30-11-2008
10720090@unknown@formal@none@1@S@It also integrates all learning schemes and attribute evaluators of the [[Weka (machine learning)|Weka]] learning environment.@1@16@@oe@30-11-2008
